1
00:00:00,618 --> 00:00:18,180
THREE, DECEMBER SIX, NINETEEN NINETY FIVE. TALKING TODAY WITH SURVIVOR ARIE GILINSKI. AND YOU s- du host geganen tsurik tsum lager. host nisht gefunen dayn froy. z- zog mir vos hot pasirt dem tsayt?

2
00:00:12,363 --> 00:00:13,303
&lt;gegangen&gt;

3
00:00:14,675 --> 00:00:15,969
UNK &lt;mayn froy&gt;.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:18,839
ikh vel dertseyln.

5
00:00:18,540 --> 00:00:21,151
di rusishe soldatn hot gekumen.

6
00:00:21,003 --> 00:00:22,196
yo, zey zaynen arayn...

7
00:00:21,459 --> 00:00:23,411
arayngegangen INTO Vilne.

8
00:00:23,113 --> 00:00:24,897
in Vilne zaynen zey arayngegangen.

9
00:00:25,172 --> 00:00:27,749
far vos hostu geganen tsurik tsum lager?

10
00:00:27,618 --> 00:00:30,009
kh'hob gevelt a-, di froy hob ikh gevelt aroysnemen.

11
00:00:33,137 --> 00:00:35,380
zog mir vos hot pasirt yetst.

12
00:00:35,465 --> 00:00:37,080
az ikh bin gekumen tsu geyn in lager,

13
00:00:37,794 --> 00:00:41,653
ikh ze mayn froy zitst un vasht di fis, a lebedike.

14
00:00:43,042 --> 00:00:44,550
farshtendlekh, mir hobn zikh arumgekhapt zikh.

15
00:00:44,630 --> 00:00:46,220
zogt zi azoy, zogt zi:

16
00:00:46,299 --> 00:00:47,830
"ikh hob gevust az du lebst."

17
00:00:48,030 --> 00:00:49,180
HO-, vi host...

18
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:52,605
o, zi hot mir gefunen mayne zakhn vos ikh hob ibergeton,

19
00:00:54,078 --> 00:01:01,447
hot zi gefunen mit velkhe ikh bin antlofn gevorn, di zakhn, hot zi zey gefunen, hot zi farshtanen, kh'bin gekumen zikh iberton di zakhn, hot zi gevust az ikh leb.

20
00:01:05,098 --> 00:01:07,017
nu, mir hobn zikh bagegnt zikh,

21
00:01:07,663 --> 00:01:12,450
un zi hot gehat mit zikh di ts-. ah. itster azoy: ven zi iz gelegn oyfn baheltenish

22
00:01:13,130 --> 00:01:17,057
mit di tsvey kinder zaynen dortn geven, di tsvey kinder vos ikh hob geratevet dem ershtn mol.

23
00:01:19,053 --> 00:01:22,575
hot di kleyn kind, di meydele, iz geven fir yor, hot zi gebetn vaser.

24
00:01:23,205 --> 00:01:31,435
hot zikh ongerufn dortn eyner az "mir hobn nit keyn vaser". zogt der tate irer: "du host dokh a tshaynik mit vaser, gib ir vaser, zi iz dokh a kind." hot er im geshosn.

25
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:34,624
a yid. in baheltenish.

26
00:01:35,321 --> 00:01:38,961
hot gegebn di froy zayne a geshrey "vos tustu?" hot er ir oykh geshosn.

27
00:01:41,210 --> 00:01:47,263
di kinder hobn zikh tsugetulyet tsu mayn froy. far vos? zey hobn ir gekent, mir flegn &lt;derekh-agev&gt; zayn tsuzamen, ikh hob zey geratevet.

28
00:01:48,382 --> 00:01:50,014
un zey hobn mir shoyn nit opgelozt.

29
00:01:52,196 --> 00:01:54,469
zogt mayn froy, zogt zi:

30
00:01:55,149 --> 00:01:58,738
"loz di kinder, gib zey a bisl vaser, zi khalesht dokh far vaser."

31
00:01:59,047 --> 00:02:00,679
zogt er: "es vet ir gor nit shatn.

32
00:02:02,642 --> 00:02:04,848
un oyb du vest a sakh reydn vel ikh dir oykh shisn."

33
00:02:05,358 --> 00:02:12,187
zogt zi: "du vest mir take shisn, ober mayn man lebt, er vet dir gut batsoln derfar." azoy vi der harts hot ir gezogt. un er hot ir nit getshepet.

34
00:02:13,745 --> 00:02:15,326
un zi iz aroys mit di kinder

35
00:02:16,682 --> 00:02:18,213
un zi hot zikh bahaltn zikh.

36
00:02:19,584 --> 00:02:21,790
ven ikh hob ir getrofn, iz zi aroys mit di kinder.

37
00:02:23,887 --> 00:02:31,577
nokh dem, az mir zaynen gekumen, bin ikh m- iz- k- iz gekumen, ikh, der bruder un zi, mir zaynen avekgegangen in di zelbe hoyz vu mir hobn a mol gelebt.

38
00:02:31,312 --> 00:02:33,028
mit di tsvey kinder?

39
00:02:32,274 --> 00:02:36,926
mit di tsvey kinder, yo. o, s'iz geven tsores, nit geven keyn esn far zey, vayl mir hobn aleyn nit gehat vos tsum esn.

40
00:02:37,185 --> 00:02:38,412
s'iz geven milkhome-tsayt.

41
00:02:39,581 --> 00:02:50,607
mir zaynen avek mit zey, mit di kinder, un mir hobn nit gehat vos tsum esn. hobn mir di kleyne, hobn mir zikh vi es iz oysgeporet far ir. farn groysn hobn mir nit gehat vos tsum esn, hobn mir im avekgegebn in a kinder-heym, iz geven aza.

42
00:02:50,607 --> 00:02:53,515
er iz geven nay- nayn yor. NO, di k- di kleyne iz geven mit undz.

43
00:02:50,668 --> 00:02:51,692
beyde?

44
00:02:52,642 --> 00:02:53,514
di kleyne,

45
00:02:53,790 --> 00:02:54,561
di meydl.

46
00:02:54,107 --> 00:02:55,574
di meydl iz geven mit undz.

47
00:02:56,591 --> 00:02:59,404
biz lang vi azoy vi me hot gedarft forn in Yisroel.

48
00:02:59,713 --> 00:03:03,859
s'rov hobn zey di kinder avekgetr-, kh'hob gehe-, s'iz geven ilegal. di kinder hot men nit gekent nemen.

49
00:03:04,050 --> 00:03:05,648
ilegal far dir oykhet.

50
00:03:05,180 --> 00:03:07,390
ilegal, yo, ilegal.

51
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,698
aroys ilegal fun Vilne oykh.

52
00:03:10,057 --> 00:03:12,769
mir hobn zi nit gekent nemen, hobn mir di meydl oykh avekgegebn in a kinder-heym.

53
00:03:13,533 --> 00:03:16,380
un me hot ir gebrakht in a por yor arum in Varshe,

54
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:18,946
in Varshe iz zi geshtorbn.

55
00:03:19,237 --> 00:03:20,126
di meydl?

56
00:03:19,271 --> 00:03:24,853
kh'hob dertseylt far dem, yo, a a CANCER oyfn kop hot zi bakumen, tsu tsen yor iz zi geshtorbn. tsen yor iz zi geshtorbn.

57
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:24,310
tsen yor alt.

58
00:03:26,105 --> 00:03:28,260
shoyn. un mir hobn onge-. yo.

59
00:03:27,152 --> 00:03:29,105
AND ir bruder? der bruder?

60
00:03:28,873 --> 00:03:30,792
der bruder, der bruder iz geblibn lebn.

61
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:34,808
der bruder lebt, er iz in Yisroel. afile, vu, er &lt;hot do&gt; geboyt a familye.

62
00:03:32,636 --> 00:03:34,403
yo, du host mir gezogt.

63
00:03:35,589 --> 00:03:42,395
un mir hobn vayter ge-, vayter gel-, vayter mamshekh geven mitn lebn. ober vos? glaykh nokhn bafrayung bin ikh avek oyf Ponar.

64
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:44,812
Ponar vu me hot dershosn ale yidn.

65
00:03:45,714 --> 00:03:48,334
dortn hob ikh derzen a shoyderlekhn bild, hob ikh derzen dortn.

66
00:03:48,423 --> 00:03:50,536
mentshn oysgehargete...

67
00:03:49,477 --> 00:03:50,991
ven hot dos geven?

68
00:03:51,131 --> 00:03:55,210
dos iz geven in in JULY fir un fertsik.

69
00:03:55,518 --> 00:04:02,820
JULY fir un fertsik. dem tsvey un tsvantsikstn, dem fin- dray un tsvantsikstn, zaynen arayn di rusn, JULY, in Vilne, bafrayt,

70
00:04:03,163 --> 00:04:05,976
un glaykh nokh dem zaynen mir avek oyf Ponar zen vos dortn iz.

71
00:04:07,010 --> 00:04:09,486
dortn gelegn mentshn in di kleydung

72
00:04:09,778 --> 00:04:19,577
dershosene, geven azoy: yidn, un litviner un polyakn. un oykh gaystlekhe. veyst vos ga-...? Ponar. oykh gaystlekhe, veyst vos a gaystlekher iz?

73
00:04:16,359 --> 00:04:18,497
in PONARY? dos iz PONARY?

74
00:04:19,802 --> 00:04:21,198
 galokhim.

75
00:04:23,227 --> 00:04:27,981
ir veyst vos a galekh iz, yo? galokhim geven, farbundn di hent oyf hintn mit shtekhl-drot,

76
00:04:28,948 --> 00:04:30,563
un geshosn in di kep alemen.

77
00:04:32,745 --> 00:04:37,516
az mir zaynen dortn gekumen, mir zaynen geven a grupe vilner yidn, az mir zaynen dortn gekumen hobn mir gezogt "genug. STOP."

78
00:04:38,212 --> 00:04:43,877
yetst, vos zol nit zayn, forn mir &lt;me zo-&gt; in a plats mir zoln zikh kenen farteydikn mit di eygene gever.

79
00:04:44,861 --> 00:04:46,780
un mir hobn bashlosn, mir forn in Yisroel.

80
00:04:47,645 --> 00:04:50,543
dos iz geven in nayntsn fir un fer-, di milkhome iz gegangen.

81
00:04:49,755 --> 00:04:52,416
vi host gegangen tsu tsu ISRAEL?

82
00:04:52,607 --> 00:04:54,897
PALESTINE hot geven, dem tsayt.

83
00:04:54,092 --> 00:04:54,931
vos?

84
00:04:55,408 --> 00:04:57,445
hot geven PALESTINE dem tsayt!

85
00:04:57,163 --> 00:05:01,546
yo, ikh hob do di bi- b- biletn, ikh hob bavizn az ikh bin gekumen in PALESTINE in yener tsayt.

86
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:06,338
mir hobn bashlosn tsu forn. ober vi fort men? s'iz dokh a milkhome.

87
00:05:06,782 --> 00:05:13,088
vu der front iz gegangen, der rusisher front iz gegangen, zaynen mir nokhgegangen. vos me hot ayngenumen a shtot, zaynen mir oykh arayn &lt;in der shtot dortn&gt;.

88
00:05:13,278 --> 00:05:16,277
zaynen mir avek oyf Rumenye. me hot ayngenumen Rumenye, zaynen mir avek oyf Rumenye.

89
00:05:16,687 --> 00:05:20,951
nokh dem ayngenumen Poyln, avek oyf Poyln. nokh dem Ungarn, avek in Ungarn.

90
00:05:21,294 --> 00:05:23,736
un biz mir zaynen gekumen in Estraykh, in Vin.

91
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:28,934
in Vin hobn mir zikh getrofn mit di englishe armey. di rusishe armey mit di englishe hobn zikh getrofn in Vin.

92
00:05:30,272 --> 00:05:31,955
az mir zaynen dort gekumen

93
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:35,835
zaynen mir ariber oyfn englishn zayt

94
00:05:36,954 --> 00:05:40,122
un dortn hobn mir getrofn di yidishe brigade fun Yisroel.

95
00:05:42,050 --> 00:05:45,336
un zey hobn undz geholfn avektsuforn in Italye, alemen.

96
00:05:46,607 --> 00:05:50,973
in Italye zaynen mir geven a, epes a shtik tsayt, ikh gedenk nit vifl. dortn iz mayn froy vider krank gevorn.

97
00:05:52,243 --> 00:05:57,199
ikh hob gehat tsores: keyn gelt hob ikh nit gehat, keyn shprakh hob ikh nit gekent, un zi iz gelegn in shpitol,

98
00:05:58,082 --> 00:05:59,596
ober m'iz durkhgekumen.

99
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,113
in a gevisn tog hot men gezo-

100
00:06:02,490 --> 00:06:03,340
in Italye?

101
00:06:03,113 --> 00:06:05,873
in Italye, ye. in a gevisn tog hot men gezogt

102
00:06:06,755 --> 00:06:08,792
"me fort in Palestine, fort men.

103
00:06:09,371 --> 00:06:10,800
greyt zikh tsu, me fort."

104
00:06:12,341 --> 00:06:14,091
me hot undz aroyfgezetst oyf a shif.

105
00:06:15,378 --> 00:06:16,740
di shif iz geven,

106
00:06:16,998 --> 00:06:22,967
he, di shif, a kleyne shif iz zi geven, s'iz geven a frakht-shif, veyst dokh vos iz a frakht-shif, yo? vos me firt skhoyre, vos me firt.

107
00:06:23,597 --> 00:06:25,482
me hot zi ibergearbet tsu firn di mentshn.

108
00:06:26,162 --> 00:06:28,148
fir mentshn zaynen gelegn eyne oyf di andere.

109
00:06:28,997 --> 00:06:29,870
oyf zek

110
00:06:30,498 --> 00:06:32,535
vifl mentshn hot gegangen mit dir?

111
00:06:33,317 --> 00:06:34,325
in di shif.

112
00:06:34,025 --> 00:06:39,411
in di shif, ikh meyn a, ah, por hundert mentshn iz geven, ver hot gekent tseyln? ver hot gevust dortn? &lt;me hot zikh arayngeganvet&gt;

113
00:06:38,075 --> 00:06:40,710
vi lang hot genemen?

114
00:06:39,559 --> 00:06:41,136
a vokh tsayt zaynen mir geforn.

115
00:06:40,710 --> 00:06:41,729
a vokh tsayt?

116
00:06:41,737 --> 00:06:44,483
a vokh tsayt zaynen mir geven oyfn vaser, biz vanen di englender hobn undz gekhapt.

117
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:47,940
englishe tsvey kroyzers hobn undz gekhapt,

118
00:06:48,183 --> 00:06:52,734
arestirt, avekgefirt in Atlit, arayngezetst in a CAMP aza, Atlit.

119
00:06:54,731 --> 00:06:56,751
mir zaynen dortn geven a kurtse tsayt,

120
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:58,151
un me hot undz...

121
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,040
vi kurts?

122
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:01,915
epes a por monat zaynen mir geven, un me hot undz bafrayt.

123
00:07:03,422 --> 00:07:05,999
me hot undz bafrayt un avekgefirt in Kiryat-Khaim.

124
00:07:07,488 --> 00:07:15,162
di lage in Yisroel iz damols geven zeyer a sh-, s'iz shoyn geven in zeks un fertsiktn yor. di lage damols iz geven zeyer a shlekhte, s'iz keyn arbet nit geven, s'iz dokh nit geven keyn zakh.

125
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,913
ober me hot zikh durkhgeshpayzt.

126
00:07:18,997 --> 00:07:23,126
gezunt bin ikh geven, shtark bin ikh geven. ikh bin avek oyf tsum BUILDING arbetn.

127
00:07:23,537 --> 00:07:26,013
gearbet tsvey teg a vokh, s'iz nit geven keyn sakh arbet.

128
00:07:26,321 --> 00:07:27,615
zikh durkhgeshpayzt zikh.

129
00:07:29,966 --> 00:07:32,813
un me hot mir arayngenumen in der HAGANA.

130
00:07:34,134 --> 00:07:38,027
azoy vi ikh ken gever, ikh bin a gevezener fun der armey, hot men mir arayngenumen in der HAGANA.

131
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,200
s'iz geven zeks un fertsik.

132
00:07:42,015 --> 00:07:44,204
di froy oykhet OR n- nor dir?

133
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,372
NO, di froy nit.

134
00:07:46,807 --> 00:07:49,637
un als mitglid hob ikh gekrogn a biks fun der HAGANA,

135
00:07:49,997 --> 00:07:56,911
der biks iz geven greser far mir. er hot geshtamt fun Napoleon's tsaytn, a LEBEL hot er geheysn, a frantsoyzisher biks. er iz geven azoy hoykh iz er geven.

136
00:07:58,603 --> 00:08:06,074
ober di tsore mitn biks iz, me hot im gedarft bahaltn az shkheynim zoln nit visn. di legale, di HAGANA iz dokh geven umlegal un s'iz geven nokh yidn vos hobn gearbet far di englender.

137
00:08:06,618 --> 00:08:09,870
hob ikh oysgegrobn a grub, EXPERIENCE hob ikh shoyn,

138
00:08:10,095 --> 00:08:14,933
un bahaltn im. ober eyn mol a vokh darf men dokh im putsn, a biks muzstu reynikn, se ken nit andersh.

139
00:08:15,309 --> 00:08:19,236
fraytik az der shokhn iz avek davenen, hob ikh aroysgenumen dem biks un geputst.

140
00:08:19,916 --> 00:08:28,180
dos iz geven, azoy hot zikh geshlept ze- zeks un fer-... in zeks un fertsiktn yor iz der shvartser shabes, zaynen mir gegangen helfn. fun Yagur, oyb ir veyst, s'iz geven a "shvartser shabes", me hot aropgenumen di ale eltste.

141
00:08:28,775 --> 00:08:33,259
keyn sakh hobn mir zey nit gekent helfn vayle, mit keyn gever hot men dokh nit getort geyn,

142
00:08:33,551 --> 00:08:39,857
ober mir hobn geholfn di ki dortn baarbetn, z- di di... vos me hot gedarft arbetn. di khaveyrim hot men dokh gehat arestirt fun Yagur damols.

143
00:08:41,769 --> 00:08:48,092
dos iz geven zeks un fertsik. in zibn un fertsik hot zikh ongehoybn mit di araber. di araber hobn ongehoybn ontsufaln oyf di yidishe

144
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:51,298
KIBUTSIM, oyf di yidishe YESHUVIM...

145
00:08:52,434 --> 00:08:54,775
shtendik flegt men undz aroysshikn tsu hilf.

146
00:08:55,134 --> 00:08:59,213
s'iz geven in Yoknam iz geven, Mishmar-Haemek iz geven,

147
00:09:00,467 --> 00:09:04,326
fargesn, nokh a kibuts iz geven vos me hot undz geshikt. mir zaynen gegangen tsu im. mir hobn damols geheysn,

148
00:09:05,411 --> 00:09:08,308
mir hobn damols geheysn nit KHISH,

149
00:09:08,651 --> 00:09:11,076
HAGANA MERKHAVIT, s'heyst

150
00:09:11,807 --> 00:09:14,013
di arumike farteydikung, hot es geheysn.

151
00:09:14,895 --> 00:09:16,628
dos iz geven in zibn un fertsik.

152
00:09:18,118 --> 00:09:19,851
ende zibn un fertsik,

153
00:09:21,712 --> 00:09:23,496
s'iz geven in elftn monat, &lt;iz UNK geven&gt;

154
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,601
ende zibn un fertsik hot men undz avekgeshikt

155
00:09:26,842 --> 00:09:29,385
in BEYT SEFER KADURI, vi ikh hob dir bilder bavizn.

156
00:09:29,964 --> 00:09:35,440
dortn durkhgeyn a kurs PIKUD KRAVI, dos heyst s- oyf milkhome tsu haltn

157
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:37,351
ober lang hot er nit ongehaltn

158
00:09:37,592 --> 00:09:41,030
vayle me- me hot undz gedarft hobn tsu hilf tsu di KIBUTSIM.

159
00:09:41,388 --> 00:09:44,944
hot men undz avekgeshikt tsu bafrayen Tverye, me zol helfn bafrayen Tverye.

160
00:09:46,265 --> 00:09:47,576
bafrayt Tverye,

161
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:51,187
ober fun tsvey zaytn, tsvey zaytn zaynen geven di araber.

162
00:09:51,834 --> 00:09:57,330
un nokh dem hot men gezogt "SURYA greyt zikh aroptsugeyn Eyn-Gev, &lt;vi&gt; der kibuts fun der anderer zayt Tverye, Eyn-Gev."

163
00:09:57,588 --> 00:09:58,967
muz ikh forn in Eyn-Gev.

164
00:10:01,048 --> 00:10:02,596
mir zaynen ariber in Eyn-Gev,

165
00:10:02,853 --> 00:10:06,105
hot men gegebn mentshn tsu lernen oyf mashin-gever.

166
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:13,598
ober tsum badoyern iz ni- keyn mashinen iz nit..., s'iz geven alte tsebrokhene keylim, me hot nit gekent arbetn, ober... vos me hot gekent hot men gemakht.

167
00:10:15,645 --> 00:10:20,973
un nokh dem hobn zey gezogt az di yardeyner greytn zikh ontsufaln oyfn kibuts Gesher.

168
00:10:21,382 --> 00:10:25,174
der kibuts Gesher shteyt lebn di elektrostantsye,

169
00:10:25,922 --> 00:10:28,954
Rutenberg's elektrostantsye, oyfn Yardn shteyt dos.

170
00:10:30,073 --> 00:10:32,262
mir zaynen gekumen tsvelf bay nakht in kibuts,

171
00:10:33,515 --> 00:10:34,371
un

172
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:40,806
me hot undz gezogt mir zoln arayngeyn in TAYGERT iz do, di MISHTARA, di politsey, TAYGERT.

173
00:10:40,923 --> 00:10:44,394
arayngeyn dortn, nemen shenikes, yeder zol nemen a shenik,

174
00:10:44,771 --> 00:10:46,690
mit a biks, un arayngeyn dortn.

175
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:50,942
