NO. OKAY. THEN I THINK WHAT WE'LL DO NOW IS LOOK AT THE PHOTOGRAPHS, AND MISTER GILINSKI WILL EXPLAIN

360
00:21:52,191 --> 00:21:54,337
WHAT THEY ARE AND WHAT THEY MEAN,

361
00:21:54,337 --> 00:22:00,048
SO THAT WE WILL HAVE A COMPLETE TAPE WHICH WILL HAVE EVERYTHING ON IT THAT THAT YOU HAVE RIGHT NOW.

362
00:22:00,086 --> 00:22:03,174
AND THANK YOU FOR JOINING US FOR THIS PART OF THE INTERVIEW.

363
00:22:05,492 --> 00:22:08,406
bite, zog mir ver dos iz.

364
00:22:05,627 --> 00:22:06,381
yo,

365
00:22:08,501 --> 00:22:15,966
dos iz mayn froy, velkhe ikh hob geheyrat in nayntsn zibn un draysik, mir hobn gelebt tsuzamen biz nayntsn tsvey un akhtsik un zi iz geshtorbn in Yisroel.

366
00:22:16,595 --> 00:22:17,467
nomen?

367
00:22:17,777 --> 00:22:19,510
SARA Gilinski.

368
00:22:19,683 --> 00:22:24,842
AND ven hostu dos genumen? kenst undz zogn?

369
00:22:23,582 --> 00:22:30,394
ah, di foto iz genumen gevorn in Yisroel in nayntsn akht un fertsik, azoy, zibn un fertsik.

370
00:22:33,892 --> 00:22:40,839
MISTER Gilinski, tu mir a toyve un z- bite vos iz dos AND ver iz dos?

371
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:47,691
dos iz an I.D. CARD fun di englender in nayntsn zeks un fertsik, un ikh bin dortn aleyn oyf di karte.

372
00:22:48,135 --> 00:22:50,378
vos hostu geton...

373
00:22:48,202 --> 00:22:52,399
dos iz mit fert-, mit mit mit fufts-, nayn un fertsik yor tsurik.

374
00:22:52,513 --> 00:22:54,576
vos hostu geton mit dem kart?

375
00:22:54,767 --> 00:22:58,002
NO, dos iz I.D., on derin hostu nit gekent lebn in PALESTINE.

376
00:22:58,209 --> 00:23:03,452
host gedarft hobn an I.D.-karte, anit bistu geven umlegal. zey hobn aroysgeshikt, di englender.

377
00:23:05,752 --> 00:23:08,008
bite, zog mikh: vos iz dos?

378
00:23:09,414 --> 00:23:11,788
dos iz nokh di tsveyte HAFUGA,

379
00:23:12,333 --> 00:23:16,057
bay di tsveyte HAFUGA hobn mir gekrogn mashin-gever fun Tshekhye.

380
00:23:18,375 --> 00:23:20,378
dos iz zeyer a gute mashin-gever.

381
00:23:20,687 --> 00:23:26,976
dos heyst BESA. un ikh hob demonstrirt far di soldatn vi tsu arbetn mit derinen.

382
00:23:27,774 --> 00:23:30,705
un ven host hot dos genemt?

383
00:23:31,183 --> 00:23:32,241
velkhn yor?

384
00:23:32,617 --> 00:23:34,837
vi alt iz dos PHOTOGRAPH?

385
00:23:34,895 --> 00:23:36,848
dos iz fun akht un fertsiktn yor.

386
00:23:38,253 --> 00:23:39,244
sheynem dank.

387
00:23:42,455 --> 00:23:45,540
vos iz dos, zog undz, bite.

388
00:23:44,683 --> 00:23:46,247
dos iz a bild

389
00:23:46,691 --> 00:24:03,240
fun dem barimtn BEYT SEFER KADURI vu Moyshe DAYAN, un YIGAL ALLON, un Rabin, ale groyse firer hobn zikh dortn gelernt. in nayntsn zibn un fertsik hot men undz geshikt oyf a kurs, PIKUD KRAVI heyst dos, vi ontsufirn mitn kamf.

390
00:24:03,819 --> 00:24:30,173
un vi ir zet oyfn bild, in yener tsayt iz nokh nit geven keyn armey: es gefinen zikh mentshn in farsheydene ontuen zikh, in farsheydene gever hobn zey in hant, eyner a STEN, eyner a biks, eyner a revolver. eyner a hitl fun di politsey, eyner a hitl fun militer, un eyner on a hitl. afile oybn shteyt a meydl mit a STEN, gor-gor oybn. ikh gefin zikh der driter in di tsveyte rey fun linkn zayt.

391
00:24:35,983 --> 00:24:37,851
bite, zog mir vos dos iz.

392
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:42,745
der bild iz genumen gevorn in Sedzhere in nayntsn akht un fertsik,

393
00:24:42,969 --> 00:24:46,305
dos iz a sport-farmestung tsvishn di COMPANIES.

394
00:24:47,662 --> 00:24:48,729
AND du bist?

395
00:24:48,333 --> 00:25:00,310
vi ir zet, bin ikh fun rekhtn zayt, der ershter. ir vet a kuk ton oyf di odern vi s'iz ongeshtrengt, fun mayn haldz, vet ir zen az ikh bin geven shtark farinteresirt me zol gevinen di sport-farmestung.

396
00:25:01,397 --> 00:25:02,354
sheynem dank.

397
00:25:05,531 --> 00:25:07,804
zog mir vos dos iz, bite.

398
00:25:08,028 --> 00:25:11,769
der bild, der letster bild: mayn arbet bay SOLEL-BONE.

399
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:18,857
dos iz geven an arbet in Nitseret. ikh hob geboyt a kloyster velkher hot geheysn di Gute Bsure, der guter onzog.

400
00:25:19,098 --> 00:25:29,387
&lt;s'iz&gt; a gantse historye fun danet: du zest oybn, fun linkn zayt, shtey ikh ongeton in di tunkele zakhn. un hinter undz shteyt a galekh velkher iz geven farantvortlekh far der arbet dortn.

401
00:25:34,944 --> 00:25:36,986
bite, zog mir vos dos iz.

402
00:25:36,834 --> 00:25:39,124
dos iz a bild vos iz genumen gevorn

403
00:25:39,568 --> 00:25:41,807
in in may

404
00:25:42,622 --> 00:25:47,207
in may nayntsn finf un nayntsik, in hoyz fun di partizaner.

405
00:25:48,123 --> 00:25:54,075
mir hobn gefayert dem fuftsiktn yortsu-, fuftsiktn yortog nokhn bafrayen zikh fun Hitlern.

406
00:25:55,891 --> 00:25:57,000
AND ir nomen?

407
00:25:57,388 --> 00:25:59,189
ah, ir nomen iz Lize Kurtser.

408
00:26:00,392 --> 00:26:01,568
sheynem dank.

409
00:26:01,944 --> 00:26:03,677
bite, zog mir vos dos iz.

410
00:26:03,395 --> 00:26:13,937
dos iz a dokument aroysgegebn gevorn in Lublin ven di ershte poylishe regirung iz geshtanen in Lublin. Varshe iz nokh nit geven farnumen, zaynen mir geforn in Lodzh. a erloybenish tsu forn in Lodzh.

411
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:21,159
dos iz a erloybenish tsu trogn a revolver.

412
00:26:22,548 --> 00:26:23,565
a kolt.

413
00:26:27,324 --> 00:26:33,056
dos iz a foto, di bafrayung fun fun militer, fun TSAHAL, in nayntsn nayn un fertsik,

414
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:35,841
vu es shteyt geshribn az ikh hob bakumen

415
00:26:36,032 --> 00:26:39,655
dem oystseykhenung, OT KOMIYUT un OT SINAY.

416
00:26:46,123 --> 00:26:46,726
yo.

417
00:26:47,017 --> 00:26:51,771
dos iz a dokument aroysgegebn gevorn fun a komisye fun doktoyrim

418
00:26:52,653 --> 00:26:57,576
az ikh bin tsvey un draysik mit tsvey tsentl protsent a invalid, a krigs-invalid.

419
00:27:05,428 --> 00:27:11,751
dos iz di COMPANY vu ikh hob gearbet tsvantsik yor baym BUILDING. in der tsayt hob ikh gearbet baym boyen hayzer,

420
00:27:11,942 --> 00:27:18,501
fabrikn, a SYNAGOGUE, un afile a kloyster iz mir gelungen tsu boyen, UNK hob ikh mir geboyt in derinen.

421
00:27:21,881 --> 00:27:23,884
dos iz an erloybenish arayntsugeyn

422
00:27:24,142 --> 00:27:26,432
tsu Eykhman's protses in Yerusholaim,

423
00:27:26,690 --> 00:27:28,508
vu ikh bin geven dortn an eydes.

424
00:27:29,053 --> 00:27:35,477
dos derloybenish arayntsugeyn. dortn iz geven zeyer shtreng arayntsugeyn. me hot dray mol durkhgekontrolirt di mentshn eyder me hot zey arayngelozn dortn.

425
00:27:37,702 --> 00:27:40,162
bite, MISTER ZILINSKI, zog mir vos dos iz.

426
00:27:39,708 --> 00:27:53,398
dos iz a dokument velkher der tson-tekhniker, velkher iz geven tsuzamen mit mir in nayntsn finf un fertsik in Vilne hot mir gemakht naye tseyner oyf dem plats vos Geshtapo hot mir oysgeharg- oysgehakt baym forshn mir vu nokh yidn zaynen.

427
00:27:53,589 --> 00:28:05,418
un efsher iz, efsher vel ikh zey geyn vayzn vu, veln zey mir shenken dem lebn. ober ikh hob geshvign un gornit gezogt, hobn zey mir geshlogn. zey hobn mir afile tsebrokhn dem aksl dem rekhtn, velkhe ikh layd nokh oyfn hayntikn tog.

